Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.88,0:04:50.81,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被丢在这里已经三周了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.80,0:04:53.62,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道M作战计划成功了没
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.23,0:04:57.59,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明哥哥在冥王星军战斗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.16,0:04:59.43,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我却在这种地方…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.04,0:05:02.26,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.38,0:05:03.81,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.05,0:05:07.94,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到我们登场了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.12,0:05:19.74,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.86,0:05:29.66,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 古代
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.03,0:05:30.75,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,逃脱了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.54,0:05:42.01,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那个
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.81,0:05:55.24,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.66,0:06:01.15,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是个女人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.44,0:06:05.09,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 真是个漂亮的人
