Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.31,0:06:21.30,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「矶风」被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.54,0:06:23.05,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别退缩 开火
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.77,0:06:44.70,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「钿女」已经成功回收「天照」
