Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.19,0:06:54.31,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军驱逐舰从左舷上方接近 好快
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.35,0:07:04.44,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,瞄准 重合
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.56,0:07:07.05,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,二号 一号 射击
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.14,0:07:12.18,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命中 击毁
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.31,0:07:12.73,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.00,0:07:15.74,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌舰被击沉
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.28,0:07:17.97,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敌军舰队重整队形
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:22.19,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,命令全军撤退 残存的友军舰船有多少
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:24.87,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只有本舰和一艘驱逐舰
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.35,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是谁的船
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.95,0:07:28.52,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,古代三佐的「雪风」号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.24,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「雾岛」发来撤退信号
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.79,0:07:33.27,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,撤退？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.47,0:07:38.21,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,「现在开始撤退 跟上我们」
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.86,0:07:39.90,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,脱离战线
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.30,0:07:41.13,sub-cn,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,右满舵
